### 3. CREATE DIARY ENTRY
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/diaries/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "My fourth diary entry",
  "content": "Today was MERN Frontend development!"
}

### 4. GET ALL DIARIES
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diaries/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. GET DIARY BY ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diaries/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. UPDATE DIARY
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/diaries/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "content": "Updated content here"
}

